<h1> <a NAME="research"> Research </a> </h1> <br>

<h2> Current research interests: </h2> 
  <ul>
  <li> <b> Networks: </b> Routing, load balancing, queueing theory,
  performance evaluation and optimization.
  <li> <b> Simulation: </b> Optimization in simulation, stochastic 
  optimization methods, fast simulation, data structures for simulation,
  applications to networking problems.
  <li> <b> Databases: </b> data structures, spatial and image databases.
  </ul>

 <strong> <!WA17><a href="http://www.cs.wm.edu/~simha/research/research.html"> CV and publications </a> 
 </strong>

